901
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:55,560
It's too late.

902
00:35:55,580 --> 00:35:56,260
I'm leaving.

903
00:35:56,260 --> 00:35:57,620
Put them in your pocket.

904
00:35:59,940 --> 00:36:01,140
Where are you going?

905
00:36:01,160 --> 00:36:02,690
Dad, I'm not eating either.

906
00:36:02,730 --> 00:36:04,290
Take two eggs with you.

907
00:36:04,320 --> 00:36:04,860
Come on.

908
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:24,870
Just get to the point.

909
00:36:27,170 --> 00:36:29,500
