910
00:36:30,200 --> 00:36:31,800
Can we settle this?

911
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:39,750
Where did you get it?

912
00:36:39,900 --> 00:36:41,960
It's not good for you to know too much.

913
00:36:49,710 --> 00:36:50,360
Is it real?

914
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:51,520
Do you want it or not?

915
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:57,760
[Take all risks. Bend over backwards for friends.]

916
00:37:01,150 --> 00:37:02,950
I'll trust you for the last time.

917
00:37:03,190 --> 00:37:04,620
I forgive you

918
00:37:04,650 --> 00:37:05,840
