924
00:37:13,630 --> 00:37:14,500
Stop saying

925
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,720
ending our friendship.

926
00:37:15,720 --> 00:37:18,840
We're gonna make it big this time.

927
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:09,340
What are you doing?

928
00:38:09,410 --> 00:38:10,470
Focus on your exam.

929
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:12,150
Miaomiao.

930
00:38:30,240 --> 00:38:30,960
It's not my fault.

931
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:31,680
I really didn't know

932
