936
00:38:37,390 --> 00:38:41,080
From now on, we are no longer friends.

937
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:53,990
Tell me.

938
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:57,060
Who are you blaming this time?

939
00:38:57,080 --> 00:38:57,880
The stairs.

940
00:39:01,860 --> 00:39:02,430
Okay.

941
00:39:04,530 --> 00:39:05,990
Let's end our friendship.

942
00:39:06,750 --> 00:39:08,400
Didn't we agree that don't mention

943
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:10,400
this topic when something's wrong?

944
00:39:14,660 --> 00:39:16,260
You betrayed me as a traitor.

945
00:39:16,630 --> 00:39:18,200
Then you cheated me with fake exam papers,

946
00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:19,760
