948
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:23,340
Everything was just an accident.

949
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:24,520
Okay.

950
00:39:25,640 --> 00:39:26,480
Little Beard.

951
00:39:26,990 --> 00:39:27,590
Enough.

952
00:39:27,610 --> 00:39:29,610
Aren't you too old for this? Stop it.

953
00:39:29,790 --> 00:39:30,500
Si.

954
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:33,050
I take full responsibility.

955
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:33,910
Although everything was an accident,

956
00:39:33,910 --> 00:39:34,960
it's all my fault.

957
00:39:35,220 --> 00:39:36,210
I shouldn't be a traitor.

958
00:39:36,210 --> 00:39:37,640
I also shouldn't have played tricks.

959
00:39:37,640 --> 00:39:38,840
I will make up for my mistakes,

960
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:40,370
