965
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:43,700
It's quite...

966
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:46,520
Your point is so weird.

967
00:40:46,520 --> 00:40:47,560
Analyze

968
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:49,160
