969
00:40:49,290 --> 00:40:51,000
High school final exam paper

970
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:52,240
is so important.

971
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:52,840
How is it possible to ask

972
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:54,580
