All he could do was print some practice
papers.

974
00:40:57,560 --> 00:40:59,420
You must be tricked by Cheng Yaya.

975
00:41:02,750 --> 00:41:04,160
Cheng Yaya

976
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:06,640
