977
00:41:07,050 --> 00:41:08,580
He was taking revenge on me.

978
00:41:08,580 --> 00:41:10,320
No wonder he stayed in the bathroom

979
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:11,880
for so long that day.

980
00:41:13,010 --> 00:41:14,670
Why did he take revenge on you?

981
00:41:17,600 --> 00:41:19,000
I planned to report to Fang

982
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:20,660
