984
00:41:22,910 --> 00:41:24,570
But he didn't go to the arcade.

985
00:41:24,590 --> 00:41:25,390
He went to rob a tomb.

986
00:41:25,390 --> 00:41:26,790
So she caught me instead.

987
00:41:28,520 --> 00:41:29,270
That mischievous boy

988
00:41:29,270 --> 00:41:30,870
must knew my real intention.

989
00:41:34,810 --> 00:41:36,490
Why am I the one who got hurt

990
00:41:36,520 --> 00:41:39,400
because of your conflict with your brother?

991
00:41:42,750 --> 00:41:44,650
Bring it on.

992
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:51,690
I can't stay in this house anymore.

993
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:54,070
Seriously?

994
00:41:54,640 --> 00:41:55,430
She just

995
00:41:56,110 --> 00:41:57,770
