1003
00:42:19,720 --> 00:42:21,000
not knowing

1004
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,240
what the outside world was like.

1005
00:42:22,240 --> 00:42:23,030
I didn't know

1006
00:42:23,030 --> 00:42:24,690
what the future would be like.

1007
00:42:25,050 --> 00:42:26,360
Everyone was welcoming

1008
00:42:26,360 --> 00:42:27,640
the return of Hong Kong.

1009
00:42:27,640 --> 00:42:28,640
But I

1010
00:42:28,850 --> 00:42:30,490
became a foolish traitor,

1011
00:42:31,200 --> 00:42:32,630
being controlled by my mother,

1012
00:42:32,630 --> 00:42:34,240
